Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.77,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,80)}#08  我們又失去了某些重要的東西
Comment: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這種大熱天吃上一杯熱騰騰的杯麵很養胃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺渾身發熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}熱天當然要吃熱乎乎的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  熱上加熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季校服真是鮮嫩欲滴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你的眼神很下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說法也很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等下  剛才這傢伙也和我一起看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只針對我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們換個話題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換什麼換啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入梅雨期後我們每晚都必須看電視呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指午夜電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實雨會持續地下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我只希望這個週末能夠放晴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令營
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}6月16日  星期四  天氣  「晴」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令營前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都是第一次參加夏令營吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個組都要買好野炊用的材料對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在猶豫做咖哩還是拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做咖哩比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就決定做咖哩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽聽我的意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩  絕對要做咖哩  野營就是要吃咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}胡蘿蔔  土豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令營期間我們要做些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天就被派去撿垃圾  沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？真的嗎  我可沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還是挺愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己動手進行野炊  還要睡在帳篷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們四人是一個組的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說要睡在同一個帳篷裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女是睡在不同的帳篷裡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？  太讓我失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來去年解散後我們在河灘上玩了一會才回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河灘的話…能游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  應該可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有人下去游過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想起了一件急事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不是要買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  她們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是旅館出身的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放心地交給天城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她可是老字號旅館的下一任老闆娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  JUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday YoungLife JUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  你去了JUNES嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我去買了點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶把晚飯買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們夏令營期間要做咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去買了材料和各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  菜菜子最喜歡咖哩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天沒法回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我能一個人看好家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那是怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次  再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}6月17日  星期五  天氣  「多雲」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令營第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖  咖  咖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(310,327)}ka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(310,327)}mimizu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水水？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(278,327)}ka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(340,327)}mimizu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子和蚯蚓？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可沒放那種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為做的時候一不小心放進去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}因為不蓋蓋子的話會把蟲子引過來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  花村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咖哩太辣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  擔心的話鳴上同學也吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  嘗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們究竟是怎麼做出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然該嘗一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時可沒這種勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩一般不是辣的就是甜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個臭死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是新穎的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像含了一嘴黏糊糊的沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的地方還軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之真是噁心死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺食材沒能很好地融合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛倒是加進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛？你們究竟加了什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩要用到澱粉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應  應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用的話黏稠度不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼澱粉和麵粉都要買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低筋麵粉和高筋麵粉  該買哪種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強力的那種比較好  有男生在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就是辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不辣的話就算不上是咖哩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡菜也很辣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有胡椒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒分黑白兩種哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是旅館出身的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏佐料也是必需的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來電視上有提到過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像說是加咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭喝咖啡  所以用咖啡牛奶就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加海鮮進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,350)\fs20}（鮮海參）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能煮出好湯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把看上去有用的東西全都買下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  我們組豈不是沒飯吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還能吃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種物體X根本入不了口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個咖哩看上去好像很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大谷…同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吃吧  如果您不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是嶄新的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,500)\an8\fs22}學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說小西同學不用做作業  這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊  羨慕死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  都發生了那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也是保健委員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  人手夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來參加夏令營沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幫家裡做事  不是挺忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡倒不是挺忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下垃圾堆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同學坐著就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  請給我一些胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺肚子的狀態很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫小西尚紀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是花村還是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是小西學姐的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟學姐在一起的時候和他說過幾次話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據熟人說  那個案件後他就變得經常獨來獨往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得把碗還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛佳同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊  居然連這種地方都能送達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定連晚飯也要拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  Nice  你們叫了外賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真機靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是隨便叫了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快吃吧  別讓諸金發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來為什麼你也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被警告說如果不來的話就讓我留級
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一年級的帳篷安靜得像在舉行葬禮一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在的話當然會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這邊我感覺比較輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二  你認識小西尚紀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚紀嗎  認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我從小就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是小西學姐的弟弟對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他上小學的時候經常一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近倒是沒怎麼說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在班上給人的感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是獨來獨往不合群嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「誰知道啊」這可是關鍵之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊  而且我和他不是一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經吃飽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想要問的事情的話  直接問他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  問題的關鍵不在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要  要問什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在班上被孤立了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你問得太直接了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次被人這麼直接地問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說這反而讓人感到心情舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實被孤立了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大家都躲在離我很遠的地方盯著我看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家顧慮得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為要給家裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要應付上門採訪的記者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解  因為我家也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居們最近也搬走了  來了新鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你必須連你姐姐的份一起好好地活下去啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他邊哭邊說著這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人感到鬱悶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛家的燒肉蓋飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎  我特別喜歡吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…  那是我的第二碗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一忍  完二同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞清楚情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  欠我一個人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在並不瞭解的情況下就說討厭你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會的話讓我們再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要抓住犯人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
