Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}推理篇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完二君的事件後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者皆為女性這一共同點就不存在了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們看漏了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此  但還有什麼共同點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼都行  再多搜集些情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  我媽好像說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生田目議員辭職後回到這個城裡繼承了家業
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在是快遞員對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山野女主播的婚外情對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他自然是沒法繼續當議員了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那傢伙有不在場證明對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像和犯人沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有沒有其他的線索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山野女主播在案發前因為婚外情的報導上了新聞對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西學姐也作為第一目擊證人上了新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等等  記得天城確實也接受過電視台的採訪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二同學也在特別節目裡出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖說我根本不願意回想起那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說所有人在消失前都上過電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與電視有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼被電視報導的人就會成為犯人的下一個目標？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是究竟是誰  又是出於什麼目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於犯人的動機我們依然一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一個勁地聊天  給我好好拾垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們今後必須更加關注電視了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能瀏覽各種節目來提防犯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令營之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是有那種喜好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著這個機會我希望你實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的貞操正面臨著危機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了我不是那種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的反應為什麼這麼激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更讓人覺得你真的是那種人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在已經能接受女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說  我們還是很難相信你…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡在你的身邊很需要勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  你不是已經接受我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:15:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就到女生的帳篷裡走一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們看看我的男子漢氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了我巽完二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被諸金知道了可是會被停學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鼻子和嘴堵上的話就能讓她停止打呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你可千萬別這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Per熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你們來幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們回不了帳篷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  完二君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然闖了進來然後就暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下我們沒法入睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則起來之後恐怕會引發騷亂對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}這裡有沒有壞學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了  是諸金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先藏在這下面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}把你們全都停學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你靠得太近了啊花村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們已經睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  在的話就給我出個聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是沒睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  給我閉上嘴好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  好像有點喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺自己一下子老了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們準備怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總  總之現在沒法出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會在明早別人起床前出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊  沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別越過這條界啊  男生們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這也太擠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做什麼奇怪的事啊  花村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們度過了一個充滿各種窘迫事件的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perosna
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}6月18日  星期六  天氣  「多雲轉晴」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏令營第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就結束了啊  夏令營
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  誰也沒有被停學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  好不容易來了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先來游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你要游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渾身酸痛就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天晚上睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有和任何人一起睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你們別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一個人游泳的話也太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個去游不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你們好像還欠我們一個人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情是欠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我們沒帶泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  嗯  真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUNES自有品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是初夏的新款式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你買東西時所說的急事就是指這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你真是太有才了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  她們到哪去換衣服了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  你的這條泳褲真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很時髦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真時髦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼直勾勾地盯著人家看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一聲不吭  快說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的泳衣都很般配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁至極
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是超乎想像的棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說內容還是有點孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們將來一定會成長為好女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  鳴上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…  完二君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至於要把人踹下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂吧  反正你們都是要下去的對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸金？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝多了  真難受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  好像順著水流過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我臭不臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又失去了某些重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  幸好我們還沒進去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我喜歡的類型  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你忘了昨天晚上的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他一個人待著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:09.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c000000}人之間的羈絆就是真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.96,0:24:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  哥哥
Comment: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.14,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}下條線索
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定會被綁架對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.97,0:24:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.83,0:24:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是犯人的犯罪預告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.90,0:24:31.45,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}下集  真正的我無人知曉
